行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🥳8.4 港島西大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356505</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxAePbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxAePbd.png&h=0487fe92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n簽咗都要🙏廣傳🙏快夠數💪唔好話冇用就唔做，唔理效果有咩都必撐，團結是力量💪<br />\n<br />\n🖕🖕🖕見指中聯辦😡😡勾結香港黑社會😡😡策劃元朗恐怖襲擊聯署🖕🖕🖕<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=309159f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n<br />\n🧐🧐【元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會】🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f59bac1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n<br />\n🤬🤬要求馬會撤銷何君堯會藉🤬🤬<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3